s del ayurveda son cero invasivas y m\u00e1s bien funcionan a trav\u00e9s de pr\u00e1cticas de armon\u00eda como alimentaci\u00f3n, ejercicios, meditaci\u00f3n, mantras, respiraci\u00f3n y m\u00e1s que permiten acceso a nuestra intuici\u00f3n y as\u00ed, escuchar a tu cuerpo y sus necesidades.\nLos antiguos m\u00e9dicos ayurv\u00e9dicos se dieron cuenta de la necesidad de preservar la alianza de la mente y el cuerpo. Por eso, crearon tantas herramientas para recordar y nutrir los aspectos m\u00e1s sutiles de nuestra humanidad. El Ayurveda busca curar la fragmentaci\u00f3n y el desorden del complejo mente-cuerpo y restaurar la integridad y la armon\u00eda de cada persona enfocado en establecer y mantener su salud f\u00edsica.\nSi quieres conocer m\u00e1s al respecto,\n[da clic aqu\u00ed.](https://www.instagram.com/ranayu_1/)", "language": null, "image": "https://i0.wp.com/thehappening.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/ayurveda-medicina.jpg?fit=1024%2C694&ssl=1", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["https://thehappening.com/", "#", "https://facebook.com/TheHappeningMX", "https://twitter.com/thehappening", "https://instagram.com/thehappeningmx", "https://play.spotify.com/user/thehappeningmx/", "https://pinterest.com/thehappeningmx", "https://thehappening.com/mailing/widget/banner.php", "https://thehappening.com/", "#trending", "https://thehappening.com/mailing/widget/banner.php", "https://thehappening.com/category/touch/", "https://thehappening.com/category/touch/", "https://thehappening.com/category/touch/decor-touch/", "https://thehappening.com/category/touch/tech-touch/", "https://thehappening.com/category/touch/toys/", "https://thehappening.com/category/touch/pets/", "https://thehappening.com/category/see/", "https://thehappening.com/category/see/", "/category/art-room", "https://thehappening.com/category/see/fashion/", "https://thehappening.com/category/see/entertainment/", "https://thehappening.com/category/see/sports/", "https://thehappening.com/category/see/traveling